DocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 29, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ysz1665703132557.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ysz1665703132557.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ysz1665703132557.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ysz1665703132557\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__uflabdbm_402598\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get a list of the names of all database fields in an entity.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__topic_d119699e1_d119700e1_d119701e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ysz1665703132557_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__codeblock_cwn_x4t_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">short uflabdbm (unsigned char* entity, unsigned char* buffer );</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__topic_d85242e1_d85243e1_d85244e1_d85245e1_d85246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d293138e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__parml_jts_y4t_zvb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the entity. To resolve ambiguity, the name can be fully qualified, for\n                  example <var class=\"keyword varname\">field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var>. You can also leave it empty to denote the current\n                  entity.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">A comma-separated list of uppercase field names. Ensure that this buffer is large\n                  enough to hold the anticipated data. (Output)</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__topic_d85247e1_d85248e1_d85249e1_d85250e1_d85251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d293138e99\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__p_d119717e1_d119718e1_d119719e1\">Zero—this function always returns zero. If there is an error, the buffer will remain empty.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__p_d119720e1_d119721e1_d119722e1\">This function has no error handling. It always returns zero. If there is an error in the entity name, there is no error message and the buffer will simply remain empty. If the buffer is too small to hold the result, the application will probably crash.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__topic_d85252e1_d85253e1_d85254e1_d85255e1_d85256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d293138e111\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__topic_d85257e1_d85258e1_d85259e1_d85260e1_d85261e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d293138e124\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__p_d119732e1_d119733e1_d119734e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uflabdbm</code> gets the names of all the\n            database fields in the specified <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> and places them in\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var> as a comma-separated list of uppercase names, for example,\n            \"NAME,STREET,NUMBER,ZIP,CITY\". Non-database fields in the entity will not be\n            included.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__p_d119735e1_d119736e1_d119737e1\">The <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> parameter can be unqualified (for example, \"PERSON\"), qualified (\"PERSON<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>PAYROLL\"), or empty (\"\") or zero to denote the current entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example gets the names of the fields in the PERSON\n            entity:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ysz1665703132557_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__codeblock_v3h_2pt_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nchar buffer[500]; /* Insure that this is large enough */\n(void)uflabdbm(\"person.payroll\", buffer);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Following a call to this function, <code class=\"ph codeph\">buffer</code> might contain\n            the following:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ysz1665703132557_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ysz1665703132557__codeblock_r11_gpt_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">NAME,PERSNUMBER,ADDRESS,ZIP,CITY</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534250\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534250\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uflabdbm Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 29, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get a list of the names of all database fields in an entity. Explain this code short uflabdbm (unsigned char* entity, unsigned char* buffer ); Copy Parameters entity Name of the entity. To resolve ambiguity, the name can be fully qualified, for example field . entity . You can also leave it empty to denote the current entity. buffer A comma-separated list of uppercase field names. Ensure that this buffer is large enough to hold the anticipated data. (Output) Return Values Zero—this function always returns zero. If there is an error, the buffer will remain empty. This function has no error handling. It always returns zero. If there is an error in the entity name, there is no error message and the buffer will simply remain empty. If the buffer is too small to hold the result, the application will probably crash. Use Library: yrtl Description uflabdbm gets the names of all the database fields in the specified entity and places them in buffer as a comma-separated list of uppercase names, for example, \"NAME,STREET,NUMBER,ZIP,CITY\". Non-database fields in the entity will not be included. The entity parameter can be unqualified (for example, \"PERSON\"), qualified (\"PERSON . PAYROLL\"), or empty (\"\") or zero to denote the current entity. The following example gets the names of the fields in the PERSON entity: Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> char buffer[500]; /* Insure that this is large enough */ (void)uflabdbm(\"person.payroll\", buffer); Copy Following a call to this function, buffer might contain the following: Explain this code NAME,PERSNUMBER,ADDRESS,ZIP,CITY Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}